snippet.title: Ingression - Official Gameplay Trailer | The MIX | Kinda Funny Spring Showcase 2024
snippet.description: Ingression is an unforgiving and mind-bending precision platformer where you'll think and platform with seamless portals. Travel to the future to save the past from an immense time paradox. Check out the trailer for Ingression to see gameplay. Ingression is coming to PC.
